pivottable
very good but uses jquery
actively maintained

react-pivot
https://github.com/davidguttman/react-pivot
good, light-weight, doesn't use jquery.

ag-Grid - by far the best grid

SlckGrid - uses jquery

jgGrid - jquery plugin (not free)

clusterize - splits the list to clusters
https://clusterize.js.org/

handsontable
https://handsontable.com/features.html

adazzle react-data-grid - uses jquery

https://github.com/okfn/recline - very good, but uses jquery

